# Implementation Plan: Strategic Switch (Ranked Solo Mod)

Implement a high-stakes, competitive solo mode called "Strategic Switch". Players transition from Linear to Circular economy through 16 questions and a SWOT analysis bridge.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The mode involves a daily limit of **4 attempts**. I will implement a live countdown timer that shows when the next attempt is available (resetting at 00:00 server time or calculated locally if preferred).
> [!NOTE]
> Questions will be hardcoded in `src/data/rankedQuestions.ts` (similar to `gameData.ts`) to maintain performance and consistency with the existing data structure, while user stats will remain in Supabase.

## Proposed Changes

### [Database & Backend]

#### [NEW] [09_strategic_switch_stats.sql](file:///c:/Users/Marko/Desktop/EIB%20WEBAPP%20-%20Copy/database_sql_scripts/09_strategic_switch_stats.sql)
- Create `user_ranked_stats` table to track:
    - `daily_attempts_left` (default 4).
    - `last_attempt_timestamp` (to calculate the reset timer).
    - `current_rp` (Ranked Points).
- Add RPC function `decrement_ranked_attempt` to atomically handle attempt logic and time tracking.

---

### [Data & Content Mapping]

#### [NEW] [rankedQuestions.ts](file:///c:/Users/Marko/Desktop/EIB%20WEBAPP%20-%20Copy/src/data/rankedQuestions.ts)
- Define `rankedLinearQuizzes` (80 questions: 40 Easy, 30 Medium, 10 Hard).
- Define `rankedCircularQuizzes` (80 questions: 40 Easy, 30 Medium, 10 Hard).
- Define `swotScenarios` (40 scenarios: 10 each for S, W, O, T).
- All content provided in English and Serbian.

---

### [UI Components]

#### [MODIFY] [StartScreen.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Marko/Desktop/EIB%20WEBAPP%20-%20Copy/src/components/StartScreen.tsx)
- Add "Strategic Switch" button below Singleplayer and Multiplayer.
- Display "Attempts Left: X/4" or a live timer if 0.

#### [NEW] [StrategicSwitchGame.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Marko/Desktop/EIB%20WEBAPP%20-%20Copy/src/components/StrategicSwitchGame.tsx)
- Implement the 3-phase flow:
    1. **Phase 1**: 8 questions from start table (3 Easy, 3 Medium, 2 Hard).
    2. **Bridge (SWOT)**: Require 3 correct categorizations in a row.
    3. **Phase 2**: Switch to opposite table + 8 questions.
- Result Screen: Calculate SRP (Ranked Points) based on final capital (Ciljeva: 500k€).

---

### [Application Logic]

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Marko/Desktop/EIB%20WEBAPP%20-%20Copy/src/App.tsx)
- Add `ranked_game` to the application state engine.
- Handle state transitions for starting and ending the ranked session.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Browser test: Starting a ranked game and verifying attempt decrement.
- Browser test: Completion of 16 questions and SRP update.

### Manual Verification
- Verify the live timer logic (changing system clock to test 00:00 reset).
- Check responsiveness of the new ranked button on mobile.
